Sentece: When the 40- and 20-kDa urea-linked conjugates were administered by i.p. injection, high relative bioavailability (46% and 99%, respectively) of alsterpaullone was observed.
Title: Poly(ethylene glycol) prodrugs of the CDK inhibitor, alsterpaullone (NSC 705701): synthesis and pharmacokinetic studies.
